       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL-CALC.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 EMPLOYEE-RECORD.
          05 EMP-ID       PIC 9(6).
          05 BASE-SALARY  PIC 9(8)V99.
          05 HOURS-WORKED PIC 9(4)V99.
          05 SSN          PIC 9(9).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           IF HOURS-WORKED > 40
               COMPUTE OVERTIME = (HOURS-WORKED - 40) * BASE-SALARY * 1.5
           ELSE MOVE 0 TO OVERTIME END-IF
           COMPUTE GROSS-PAY = BASE-SALARY + OVERTIME
           COMPUTE NET-PAY = GROSS-PAY - (GROSS-PAY * 0.28)
           DISPLAY "NET PAY: " NET-PAY
           STOP RUN.
